,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/inUMzkCRC8AcTZLTLU3OrIAiZRM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/vnTVExLEgVPqDJbWXoxntjOuxUT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/1ZcExJYILyZsSw3LxJUbNUf64xR.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:27:19.507+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":120,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In the 1940s, Malays were world-renowned for their seafaring skills. Being of Bugis descent, they navigated the sea with natural ease and were often the favored seamen for international shipping lines. Othman, a fisherman from a small village in Malacca, leaves his family behind to sail the world, with hopes to return home one day with worldly riches and deserved pride. After decades at sea, however, his low wages as a deckhand leaves him disillusioned. He contemplates returning home to his family but ended up settling down in Liverpool, England. 60 years later, his grandson, Ahmad, journeys halfway across the world in search of his grandfather."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Pulang","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Thom racconta al nipote del nonno, un marinaio partito 61 anni prima in cerca di fortuna, e gli chiede di scoprire che fine ha fatto."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Reviens","runtime":118,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81020161","overview":"Thom parle à son petit-fils de son grand-père, un marin parti 61 ans plus tôt faire fortune, et lui demande de découvrir ce que son époux est devenu."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"踏破鐵鞋回家路","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"託姆向孫子講述祖父的故事：一名為了追求財富而在 61 年前離家的水手，並要求孫子查明丈夫的下落。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"돌아오지 않는","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"왜 돌아오지 않을까. 살아있긴 한 걸까. 남편을 하염없이 기다리다 어느덧 노파가 된 여인. 그녀는 61년 전 꿈을 좇아 배를 탄 한 청년의 이야기를 손자에게 들려준다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Um Mar de Esperança","runtime":118,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Othman, um pescador de uma pequena vila em Malaca, deixa sua família para trás para navegar pelo mundo, com a esperança de um dia voltar para casa com riquezas. Mas depois de décadas no mar, porém, ele está sem dinheiro e desiludido. Ele pensa em voltar para sua família, mas acabou se estabelecendo em Liverpool, na Inglaterra. 60 anos depois, seu neto, Ahmad, viaja meio mundo em busca do avô. Inspirado em acontecimentos reais, Pulang conta a história de dois homens que anseiam por encontrar o único lugar ao qual pertencem: LAR."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"归乡的承诺","runtime":0,"tagline":"归乡的承诺","homepage":"","overview":"在 1940 年代，马来人以航海技术闻名于世。 作为武吉士血统，他们在海上航行自然自如，经常成为国际航运公司青睐的海员。 普朗讲述了一位这样的水手的故事。 奥斯曼是来自马六甲一个小村庄的渔夫，他抛下家人去环游世界，希望有一天能带着世俗的财富和应得的骄傲回家。 然而，在海上航行了几十年之后，他作为一名水手的低工资让他大失所望。 他考虑回家与家人团聚，但最终在英国利物浦定居下来。 60 年后，他的孙子艾哈迈德穿越半个地球寻找他的祖父。 受到真实事件的启发，普朗讲述了两个男人渴望找到他们唯一属于的地方：家的故事。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":8689,"adult":false,"title":"Cannibal Holocaust","video":false,"overview":"A New York University professor returns from a rescue mission to the Amazon rainforest with the footage shot by a lost team of documentarians who were making a film about the area's local cannibal tribes.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.9907,"vote_count":1814,"poster_path":"/otxZzMh53TsN7yYFqSZ3rwH1yMd.jpg","release_date":"1980-02-07","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/7QBBvE6tA1kUlo7AKeZZMygdSHp.jpg","original_title":"Cannibal Holocaust","original_language":"it"},{"id":477751,"adult":false,"title":"Bisik Pada Langit","video":false,"overview":"Wak Selamat is the father of one Siti Hajar, who wishes to study abroad. As a father, Wak does everything he can in order to fulfill her dreams. Her two brothers are also more than willing to sacrifice their own future just so their sister could further her studies. The family has high hopes for her when Siti finally makes it to Perth, Australia. However, things take a turn when Siti gets involved in an accident and Wak has to find a way to visit his daughter who is now lying in a coma.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.08,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/E4tS5hrmWj2Whhzne3W2prNuTI.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-21","vote_average":8.7,"backdrop_path":"/ekfmeMbWR0MdgB9qDpPjl2hoZsp.jpg","original_title":"Bisik Pada Langit","original_language":"ms"},{"id":466282,"adult":false,"title":"To All the Boys I've Loved Before","video":false,"overview":"Lara Jean's love life goes from imaginary to out of control when her secret letters to every boy she's ever fallen for are mysteriously mailed out.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.9641,"vote_count":8662,"poster_path":"/hKHZhUbIyUAjcSrqJThFGYIR6kI.jpg","release_date":"2018-08-17","vote_average":7.596,"backdrop_path":"/xXhta1NIKn09IXy0mfp68cabdWS.jpg","original_title":"To All the Boys I've Loved Before","original_language":"en"},{"id":351286,"adult":false,"title":"Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom","video":false,"overview":"Three years after Jurassic World was destroyed, Isla Nublar now sits abandoned. When the island's dormant volcano begins roaring to life, Owen and Claire mount a campaign to rescue the remaining dinosaurs from this extinction-level event.","genre_ids":[28,12,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.5921,"vote_count":12571,"poster_path":"/x2Us3jR6ToMJjbcPbLimYoxf6xr.jpg","release_date":"2018-06-06","vote_average":6.533,"backdrop_path":"/6WA9stUMbIkEPxn3D5SWlA8FIi7.jpg","original_title":"Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom","original_language":"en"},{"id":436969,"adult":false,"title":"The Suicide Squad","video":false,"overview":"Supervillains Harley Quinn, Bloodsport, Peacemaker and a collection of nutty cons at Belle Reve prison join the super-secret, super-shady Task Force X as they are dropped off at the remote, enemy-infused island of Corto Maltese.","genre_ids":[28,35,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.4816,"vote_count":9402,"poster_path":"/q61qEyssk2ku3okWICKArlAdhBn.jpg","release_date":"2021-07-28","vote_average":7.468,"backdrop_path":"/jlGmlFOcfo8n5tURmhC7YVd4Iyy.jpg","original_title":"The Suicide Squad","original_language":"en"},{"id":354912,"adult":false,"title":"Coco","video":false,"overview":"Despite his family’s baffling generations-old ban on music, Miguel dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol, Ernesto de la Cruz. Desperate to prove his talent, Miguel finds himself in the stunning and colorful Land of the Dead following a mysterious chain of events. Along the way, he meets charming trickster Hector, and together, they set off on an extraordinary journey to unlock the real story behind Miguel's family history.","genre_ids":[10751,16,10402,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.8389,"vote_count":20684,"poster_path":"/6Ryitt95xrO8KXuqRGm1fUuNwqF.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-27","vote_average":8.199,"backdrop_path":"/g7CHF8gTLGooTbP4GznIGwaqAGL.jpg","original_title":"Coco","original_language":"en"},{"id":495764,"adult":false,"title":"Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)","video":false,"overview":"Harley Quinn joins forces with a singer, an assassin and a police detective to help a young girl who had a hit placed on her after she stole a rare diamond from a crime lord.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.7382,"vote_count":10694,"poster_path":"/h4VB6m0RwcicVEZvzftYZyKXs6K.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-05","vote_average":6.885,"backdrop_path":"/uozb2VeD87YmhoUP1RrGWfzuCrr.jpg","original_title":"Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of One Harley Quinn)","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.7563,"vote_count":11389,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":315635,"adult":false,"title":"Spider-Man: Homecoming","video":false,"overview":"Following the events of Captain America: Civil War, Peter Parker, with the help of his mentor Tony Stark, tries to balance his life as an ordinary high school student in Queens, New York City, with fighting crime as his superhero alter ego Spider-Man as a new threat, the Vulture, emerges.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.8087,"vote_count":22879,"poster_path":"/c24sv2weTHPsmDa7jEMN0m2P3RT.jpg","release_date":"2017-07-05","vote_average":7.329,"backdrop_path":"/tPpYGm2mVecue7Bk3gNVoSPA5qn.jpg","original_title":"Spider-Man: Homecoming","original_language":"en"},{"id":166428,"adult":false,"title":"How to Train Your Dragon: The Hidden World","video":false,"overview":"As Hiccup fulfills his dream of creating a peaceful dragon utopia, Toothless’ discovery of an untamed, elusive mate draws the Night Fury away. When danger mounts at home and Hiccup’s reign a