ose nude for a charity calendar.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":3.2174,"vote_count":397,"poster_path":"/yy2cPwrnUquMCmShrf8TbYu6emd.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-02","vote_average":6.531,"backdrop_path":"/mB23ce4CxfUwSb9Y6YY8NPLyy2E.jpg","original_title":"Calendar Girls","original_language":"en"},{"id":8588,"adult":false,"title":"Shooting Dogs","video":false,"overview":"Two westerners, a priest and a teacher find themselves in the middle of the Rwandan genocide and face a moral dilemna. Do they place themselves in danger and protect the refugees, or escape the country with their lives? Based on a true story.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":0.477,"vote_count":159,"poster_path":"/9xC2yUgqPVvoHykYuigrxLyunya.jpg","release_date":"2006-03-08","vote_average":7.469,"backdrop_path":"/6PkzgNLKoK1Oy0j7L79JuBgl22r.jpg","original_title":"Shooting Dogs","original_language":"en"},{"id":8349,"adult":false,"title":"The Red Baron","video":false,"overview":"Richthofen goes off to war like thousands of other men. As fighter pilots, they become cult heroes for the soldiers on the battlefields. Marked by sportsmanlike conduct, technical exactitude and knightly propriety, they have their own code of honour. Before long he begins to understand that his hero status is deceptive. His love for Kate, a nurse, opens his eyes to the brutality of war.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,36,10752],"popularity":1.649,"vote_count":274,"poster_path":"/lUuryram6Aoa11dCgoXohR8avjU.jpg","release_date":"2008-03-29","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/lAS4vRXqpA6jrSK1vRmxbtpsCop.jpg","original_title":"Der rote Baron","original_language":"de"},{"id":470878,"adult":false,"title":"I Can Only Imagine","video":false,"overview":"Growing up in Greenville, Texas, Bart Millard suffers physical and emotional abuse at the hands of his father, Arthur. When Arthur becomes terminally ill, he finds redemption by embracing his faith and rediscovering his love for his son. Years later, Bart's troubled childhood and mended relationship with his dad inspires him to write the hit song \"I Can Only Imagine\" as singer of the Christian band MercyMe.","genre_ids":[10402,18],"popularity":2.7873,"vote_count":493,"poster_path":"/veZszwMZu8d3WMU6TJX9sV5w1Y4.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-14","vote_average":7.526,"backdrop_path":"/AjtQdUX41skfo8tthtrnJZI9bXV.jpg","original_title":"I Can Only Imagine","original_language":"en"},{"id":8848,"adult":false,"title":"The Bank Job","video":false,"overview":"Terry is a small-time car dealer trying to leave his shady past behind and start a family. Martine is a beautiful model from Terry's old neighbourhood who knows that Terry is no angel. When Martine proposes a foolproof plan to rob a bank, Terry recognises the danger but realises this may be the opportunity of a lifetime.","genre_ids":[53,80,18],"popularity":4.3729,"vote_count":2531,"poster_path":"/bfXjFTytfFTdo9WeO7lYqzkHG7g.jpg","release_date":"2008-02-28","vote_average":6.84,"backdrop_path":"/pqoYtQsD8xwKFB5FrJQAB5e7hg5.jpg","original_title":"The Bank Job","original_language":"en"},{"id":471288,"adult":false,"title":"Dreams I Never Had","video":false,"overview":"A teenage girl is held captive in the home of a wealthy family. She is befriended by the family's young gardener, himself an illegal from Mexico. Their friendship carries both of them through their hopeless, sequestered lives and ultimately inspires them to break free.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1481,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/oViL0Ixk5PVP649ciEa9tNHy66c.jpg","release_date":"2018-04-01","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/yCctV5LWdfVusw1vh6iVYeOSNwK.jpg","original_title":"Dreams I Never Had","original_language":"en"},{"id":471317,"adult":false,"title":"One Less God","video":false,"overview":"In 2008, a band of young Islamic militants from Pakistan lands in Mumbai, their primary target, the iconic Taj Mahal hotel. With Indian forces unable to regain control, for 4 days the guests must battle to survive as the terrorists seek to drive them from hiding. The harrowing events that follow will come to be known as India's 9/11 and one of the most audacious terrorist attacks in history. Yet more than a tale of monsters and men, this is a story of our shared humanity at the dark crossroads to which we have now stumbled. Inspired by true events.","genre_ids":[80,28,18,53],"popularity":0.1938,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/zdRBRzaU8YgrKQxPwGkAU1qaRkh.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-06","vote_average":6.154,"backdrop_path":"/vFb6Ot5iR5454vNB5duNoCdcA55.jpg","original_title":"One Less God","original_language":"en"},{"id":9289,"adult":false,"title":"The Longest Day","video":false,"overview":"The retelling of June 6, 1944, from the perspectives of the Germans, US, British, Canadians, and the Free French. Marshall Erwin Rommel, touring the defenses being established as part of the Reich's Atlantic Wall, notes to his officers that when the Allied invasion comes they must be stopped on the beach. \"For the Allies as well as the Germans, it will be the longest day\"","genre_ids":[10752,28,18],"popularity":3.5137,"vote_count":998,"poster_path":"/5zmvEofdIlgXrQl9A7e5IOzlnFU.jpg","release_date":"1962-09-25","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/yt9FIS2Osm97M7w4dLFkBu7YxW8.jpg","original_title":"The Longest Day","original_language":"en"},{"id":278236,"adult":false,"title":"X+Y","video":false,"overview":"A socially awkward teenage math prodigy finds new confidence and new friendships when he lands a spot on the British squad at the International Mathematics Olympiad.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.2172,"vote_count":598,"poster_path":"/jYkfSWb9rlTTzvLclCuJwm48kbl.jpg","release_date":"2014-03-13","vote_average":6.691,"backdrop_path":"/qqRzC2xkCCTTPVA7IKYf4CsPkEj.jpg","original_title":"X+Y","original_language":"en"},{"id":278270,"adult":false,"title":"Dempsey","video":false,"overview":"Nominated for two primetime Emmy Awards in 1984, this made-for-TV movie follows the true story of American boxer Jack Dempsey, who became a medi